com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.dynamictype
Interface DynamicPaletteStack

public interface DynamicPaletteStack

A representation of the model object 'Dynamic Palette Stack'. The specification of a dynamic palette stack

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Icon
  • Id
  • Label

See Also:
